subject: resource/Projekt_Herz
object: Projekt Herz (English: Project Heart)  is the first EP by German metalcore band, We Butter the Bread with Butter. It was released December 19, 2012 independently. It is also the band's first release to feature Paul Bartzsch on vocals.On Facebook, the band posted a comment on November 18, 2012 with a picture of their new album cover for "Projekt Herz" saying "It all begins Thursday".The album was hitting Nr. 10 at US Album Charts.
